@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_gdhnay(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.67
    v0 = ((0.86 / (v1 + 0.85 - v0 + 0.55)) * 0.26)
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = v2
    v0 = 0.27
    tmp = ((0.23 / wp.abs(tmp + 0.88)) * ((v1 + 0.90 + tmp + 0.07) / (v0 + 0.90 / v2 + 0.43)))
    data[tid] = v0
